name: combineLatest(_:_:)
desc: Subscribes to two additional publishers and publishes a tuple upon receiving output from any of the publishers.
declaration: func combineLatest<P, Q>(_ publisher1: P, _ publisher2: Q) -> Publishers.CombineLatest3<Self, P, Q> where P : Publisher, Q : Publisher, Self.Failure == P.Failure, P.Failure == Q.Failure
